pid":"fa3ebdc3a73c51cc6784ab1077bba6ec00cf3930","tid":143864,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T04:38:31.000Z","msg":"女仔比較難增肌，不過食唔肥又想增重都係要由負重運動開始，只要記住運動前後食碳水類食物就會特別易吸收<br />\n<br />\n初期做啲半小時就完成到嘅負重運動做就夠，負重唔一定要有啞鈴，好多運動都可以用自身重量去做，不過有啞鈴就會方便啲，運動前要有最少六成飽，運動完再食到全飽，避免高油份及脂肪類食物，最方便係食麥皮，惠康啲即食麥皮都幾抵食，可以用凍奶直接開黎食，亦可以用凍水落少少黃糖黎沖，絕對唔難食<br />\n<br />\n祝增磅愉快"},{"pid":"b37865622592354e74ee4f0ccfcd94d139e92dd3","tid":143864,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T04:43:14.000Z","msg":"幾高呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你仲瘦過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2580cb12907c9a832fd8de190003d0c9daaf3b4f","tid":143864,"uid":4010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T04:45:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾高呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你仲瘦過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n又係絲打你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我162<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"199d4c92cb3c1e3819686391b1bd6fef4b7ee027","tid":143864,"uid":20386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T04:46:05.000Z","msg":"留名學野"},{"pid":"35e861b3b263ea6eba90deec9363a2df25472fd0","tid":143864,"uid":21202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T04:47:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>幾高呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你仲瘦過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n又係絲打你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我162<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同個男仔拍拖會自然幸福肥"},{"pid":"8e6208cf54f7d5e4382764e18df81e24ea149f4a","tid":143864,"uid":35774,"like":0,"dislike":0